data.title: About Lance Featherstone
data.meta_description:
I am currently a film student studying BA Film Production at the Arts University Bournemouth (AUB). I have an avid interest in wildlife and regularly go for long walks or camping trips to various places around the UK in order to catch that once in a lifetime shot. 
	
	I use a Nikon D3100 at the moment, but hope to upgrade to something better soon!
